article_title: Western Stark County Free Clinic to close
article_text:
Free clinic by the numbers

Year opened: 1999



Patient visits: More than 20,000



No. of patients seen annually: Around 500 individuals



Value of prescriptions provided: More than $2 million...

article_metadata.description: The clinic has lost at least 170 patients — a 30 percent drop — since the beginning of the year.
article_metadata.author: Amy L. Knapp
